Entries.default: "Stelgaer blood courses through your veins! But enough to mark you the Slayer's chosen? Summon your rivals! Fight for my title!"
"The stelgaer-kin hunt well, but the Watcher hunts better! Toamowhai is pleased! I am pleased!"
"Though smaller than the mighty stelgaer, the great felines of Eora are deadly hunters! In a pack, they demand fear!"
"Luck is for the weak! May the most savage win!"
"Though kith hunters flailingly imitate their methods, the nāga use venom as a master musician plays! Are you prepared for their performance?"
"Luck is for the weak! May the most savage win!"
"The nāga's venom often offers only pyrrhic victory for those who best them, yet our contender lives to fight another day!"
"This is the truth of the jungle - as strong as you are, there is always someone stronger! How one deals with this measures the slayer!"
"Such fury from so small a hunter! Your ferocity will serve you well, Watcher."
"Luck is for the weak! May the most savage win!"
"The Engwithans forged the Fire Titan to have no weakness and no equal in battle! Prepare to relive the same fate that befell thousands of trespassers into ancient Engwith!"
"Despite its outward advantages, even the mighty Fire Titan is unable to match your strength! Your prowess reflects the Slayer!"
"A true slayer can finish a fight even when robbed of their advantages and forced to improvise!"
"Even denied your core strengths, you bring glory to the Slayer! Your ferocity transcends form! Most impressive."
"The reptilian hunters proved no match for the Watcher! Revel in your triumph, for you bring glory to all kith!"
"Long before the first hunter set arrow to bow, cold-blooded predators stalked the kith. Today you are again the quarry!"
"Luck is for the weak! May the most savage win!"
